---
<section class="quote-wrap">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="quote">
      <p>
        The powerhouse behind <span class="brand-a">independent brands</span>
        bringing the playbook
        to <span class="brand-b">market leadership</span>.
      </p>
      <a href="/work" class="see-all">See all our success stories →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .quote-wrap { padding: 1rem 0 4rem; }
  .quote {
    background: #d8d8d8;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .quote p {
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.8vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: #fff;
    max-width: 28ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .brand-a { color: var(--bp-orange); }
  .brand-b { color: var(--bp-deep); }
  .see-all {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--bp-deep);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .see-all:hover { color: var(--bp-orange); }
</style>
